    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>When Push Comes To Shove</i>, you step into the role of a robot navigating through a series of complex, mind-bending tests designed to challenge your puzzle-solving abilities. This engaging <strong>tile-based puzzle game</strong> invites players to push blocks, jump over gaps, and avoid dangerous obstacles, all while uncovering the mystery behind the tests. Whether you're a fan of <strong>block-pushing puzzles</strong> or love overcoming tricky <strong>laser traps</strong> and <strong>spike traps</strong>, this game has something for every puzzle lover.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Test Your Puzzle-Solving Skills in a Tile-Based Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a robot, your mission is simple: <strong>push blocks</strong> to clear your path, jump over short gaps, and avoid deadly traps in order to complete each level. The game’s <strong>tile-based puzzle mechanics</strong> provide a unique twist, requiring you to carefully plan your movements to progress through increasingly difficult stages. The <strong>block-pushing puzzle</strong> system makes each move essential, and one wrong step can set you back.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overcome Dangerous Obstacles Like Lasers, Pitfalls, and Traps</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While pushing blocks may seem easy at first, things aren’t as simple as they seem. Be wary of hidden dangers such as <strong>laser traps</strong>, <strong>spike traps</strong>, and <strong>pitfalls</strong> that can quickly end your progress. These dangerous obstacles add an exciting element of risk and reward to the game, keeping you engaged as you strategize each move. Will you be able to avoid the deadly traps and finish the tests unscathed?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What Are They Testing You For?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you advance through each level, you can’t help but wonder: What exactly are they testing you for? What is the true purpose behind these tests? The answer remains a mystery throughout the game, adding an extra layer of intrigue to the experience. One thing is clear, though—you have no choice but to <strong>push forward</strong> and complete the tests, regardless of the unknown forces behind them.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Why You’ll Love When Push Comes To Shove</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>When Push Comes To Shove </i>combines classic <strong>puzzle mechanics</strong> with modern twists, making it the perfect game for fans of <strong>tile-based puzzles</strong> and <strong>action-packed puzzle challenges</strong>. The game’s increasing difficulty ensures that it will keep you engaged as you progress through each level, while the mysterious narrative will keep you guessing until the very end. Whether you’re a casual gamer or a <strong>puzzle enthusiast</strong>, <i>Push Forward</i> offers hours of <strong>brain-teasing fun</strong> and challenging puzzles that will test your skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to tackle the tests, avoid the traps, and uncover the secrets behind your mission? Start pushing those blocks, avoid the lasers, and jump into the <strong>puzzle adventure</strong> today!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push Blocks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274220/extras/4ad7c4a12436198ab868d02782f2b40c.poster.avif?t=1740760990\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274220/extras/4ad7c4a12436198ab868d02782f2b40c.webm?t=1740760990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274220/extras/4ad7c4a12436198ab868d02782f2b40c.mp4?t=1740760990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump Gaps</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274220/extras/a143b36fa8dcaf432241b95fbcae898d.poster.avif?t=1740760990\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274220/extras/a143b36fa8dcaf432241b95fbcae898d.webm?t=1740760990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274220/extras/a143b36fa8dcaf432241b95fbcae898d.mp4?t=1740760990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press triggers to unlock doors</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274220/extras/5d5b5645b32835636187fab605378910.poster.avif?t=1740760990\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274220/extras/5d5b5645b32835636187fab605378910.webm?t=1740760990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274220/extras/5d5b5645b32835636187fab605378910.mp4?t=1740760990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch out for lasers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274220/extras/532db2144e16d0bc32bda22d25372d4f.poster.avif?t=1740760990\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274220/extras/532db2144e16d0bc32bda22d25372d4f.webm?t=1740760990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274220/extras/532db2144e16d0bc32bda22d25372d4f.mp4?t=1740760990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274220/extras/3a48500697d070c9b87e7448736d8d4b.poster.avif?t=1740760990\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274220/extras/3a48500697d070c9b87e7448736d8d4b.webm?t=1740760990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274220/extras/3a48500697d070c9b87e7448736d8d4b.mp4?t=1740760990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
